{"title": "WFuzz", "source": "enum", "source_label": "Enumeration", "path": "wfuzz", "html": "<h1 id=\"wfuzz\">WFuzz</h1>\n<h2 id=\"fuzz-keyword-basics\">FUZZ Keyword Basics</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Basic directory fuzzing</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With extensions</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ.php\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Status code filter (hide 404)</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Show only 200 responses</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--sc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Threads</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># No color output</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"multiple-injection-points-fuzz-fuz2z-fuz3z\">Multiple Injection Points (FUZZ / FUZ2Z / FUZ3Z)</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Two injection points</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,users.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZ/FUZ2Z\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Username + password brute</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,users.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;username=FUZZ&amp;password=FUZ2Z&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/login\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Three injection points</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,list1.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,list2.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,list3.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ/FUZ2Z/FUZ3Z<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Parameter name + value discovery</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/burp-parameter-names.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?FUZZ=FUZ2Z&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"filter-options\">Filter Options</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Hide by status code (one or more)</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>,403,400<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Show by status code</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--sc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--sc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,301,302<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Hide by number of lines</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hl<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">42</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Show by number of lines</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--sl<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Hide by number of words</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hw<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">15</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Show by number of words</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--sw<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Hide by response size (bytes/chars)</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hh<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1234</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Show by response size</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--sh<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Regex match (show if matches)</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--ss<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;admin|login|dashboard&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Regex hide (hide if matches)</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hs<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Not Found|Error&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"authentication\">Authentication</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Basic HTTP auth</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">401</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Brute force basic auth</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,users.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<span class=\"w\"> </span>file,&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">401</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>FUZZ:FUZ2Z<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Cookie-based session</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;session=abc123&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Cookie brute (session token fuzz)</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">302</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;session=FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/dashboard\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Bearer token</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Authorization: Bearer &lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple cookies</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;auth=abc123; csrf=xyz&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"headers\">Headers</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Custom header</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Fuzz header value</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;X-Custom-Header: FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/admin\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># User agent fuzzing</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Fuzzing/User-Agents/user-agents.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;User-Agent: FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">403</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/admin\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Host header fuzzing (vhost)</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--hh<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1234</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>http://&lt;ip&gt;/\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Content-Type fuzzing</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z<s