ON</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.json,json\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Proxy</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">127</span>.0.0.1:8080<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SOCKS5 proxy</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">127</span>.0.0.1:1080:SOCKS5<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Delay between requests</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-s<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">0</span>.5<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Max recursion (follow location headers)</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-R<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Limit concurrent connections</span>\nwfuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hc<span clas